["shippingservice-0", "adservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "cartservice-0", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "recommendationservice-0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-06T10:03:14Z to 2025-06-06T10:17:14Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-06 10:03:14+00:00 to 2025-06-06 10:17:14+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-1", "recommendationservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-0", "frontend-0", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-2", "adservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-0", "adservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "cartservice-0", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "recommendationservice-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "pod_cpu_usage", "request", "response", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"connection refused\",\n    \"transport\",\n    \"Error while dialing\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple instances of 'frontend' service are reporting 'connection refused' when trying to connect to a target service at IP 10.233.43.10:8080.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.43.10:8080: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的调用链数据，我已经完成了初始扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend调用RecommendationService时出现大量'connection refused'错误（状态码14），共出现4662次连接拒绝错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService响应时间显著增加，正常平均耗时约10秒，异常时段增加到11-13秒，延迟增加约15-20%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService响应时间大幅增加，GetCart操作从正常2.5秒增加到20-26秒，延迟增加8-10倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作延迟显著增加，HGET操作从正常1.5-1.7秒增加到8.6-21.7秒，延迟增加5-12倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 关键发现：\n\n1. **主要根因**: RecommendationService完全不可用，出现大量\"connection refused\"错误，这很可能是整个故障的触发点。\n\n2. **级联影响**: \n   - 由于RecommendationService故障，导致Frontend返回500错误\n   - CartService和Redis出现严重延迟，可能是由于负载转移或资源竞争\n   - ProductCatalogService也出现轻微延迟增加\n\n3. **调用链分析**:\n   - Frontend → RecommendationService: 连接被拒绝（根因）\n   - CheckoutService → CartService: 严重延迟\n   - CartService → Redis: 严重延迟\n   - Frontend → ProductCatalogService: 中等延迟\n\n建议进一步调查RecommendationService的部署状态和资源使用情况，以及Redis集群的性能状况。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对故障期间指标数据的全面扫描分析，我发现了多个显著的异常模式。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"request\", \"response\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"多实例出现高error_ratio和server_error_ratio异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0、frontend-1、frontend-2的error_ratio从0%上升到10.45%、10.2%、10.26%，server_error_ratio同样异常升高\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt响应时间显著增加，同时request和response流量大幅下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt从1662.86ms上升到6680.67ms（增长1.2倍），request从552降到85（下降1.47倍），response从541.5降到73（下降1.52倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max异常峰值显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从2030ms上升到2083.5ms，但p99值从4608.27ms飙升到58534.12ms（增长1.71倍），表明存在严重延迟峰值\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max出现异常峰值\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从2351ms上升到2389.5ms，但p99值从7793.32ms飙升到61624.77ms（增长1.55倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"request和response流量大幅下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"request从12990.5降到1866（下降1.5倍），response从10922降到1592.5（下降1.49倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-07节点\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes减少\",\n      \"evidence\": \"可用内存从8059615232字节减少到7201675264字节（下降11.24%），p99值下降49.06%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage显著下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CPU使用率从0.07降到0.01（下降1.5倍），表明该Pod可能处理能力下降\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **前端服务故障**：frontend服务的三个实例都出现了高错误率（10%+），这是最显著的异常信号。\n\n2. **核心服务性能问题**：productcatalogservice-1出现严重的响应时间恶化（rrt增长1.2倍），同时流量大幅下降，表明可能存在性能瓶颈。\n\n3. **支付和物流服务延迟峰值**：paymentservice-2和shippingservice-0都出现了极端的rrt_max峰值，p99值分别增长1.71倍和1.55倍。\n\n4. **资源使用异常**：aiops-k8s-07节点内存可用性下降，productcatalogservice-2的CPU使用率异常下降。\n\n这些异常模式表明系统存在多层次的性能问题，需要进一步深入分析各组件间的依赖关系。"}
